nodes.text: Timma Briss was a Human female from Corulag. She worked as a slicer at Boztrok spaceport until she stole some important files from docking bay owner and crime lord Pok Nar-Ten. She managed to elude the corrupt businessman by finding work with the starship mechanic Bolabo Hujaan who worked on Byblos. She was an associate of Kn'ik Th'ronik.
